name: My Daemon
original_name: ดีมอนของผม
overview: To save his mother, a kind-hearted boy and his tiny daemon friend set out on a journey across post-apocalyptic Japan as dark forces close in.

episodes.name: The Grave Journey
episodes.overview: Young Kento starts raising a tiny daemon with remarkable powers and names her Anna. But not everyone takes kindly to his new companion.

episodes.name: A Tough Decision
episodes.overview: Kento and Anna's journey is dangerous and difficult. They hitch a ride with kind but mysterious workers also traveling westward.

episodes.name: Friend or Foe
episodes.overview: With relief, Kento and Anna arrive in a vibrant truck stop town in Shizuoka. But even here, they have trouble finding a place to stay.

episodes.name: Corrupted Soul
episodes.overview: When he learns that a child is trapped after being attacked at the abandoned shopping center, Kento steps up to help.

episodes.name: The Collector
episodes.overview: While Kento and Kaede travel through Nagoya, an aircraft crash-lands nearby, and a giant, spider-like daemon suddenly begins rampaging the area.

episodes.name: Awakening
episodes.overview: While trying to save Kento from the spider daemon, Anna suddenly undergoes a transformation. Kaede calls her friend at the Peace Organization.

episodes.name: Impurity of Peace
episodes.overview: In Osaka, Kento and Kaede beg Ichinose to help them get Anna back, but sneaking into the Peace Organization headquarters won't be easy.

episodes.name: Separated
episodes.overview: As Kaede, Ichinose and Kento work to rescue Anna, Kaede and her grandfather discover they have a difference of opinion.

episodes.name: The Little Friendship
episodes.overview: After a rocky start, Kento and Kouya Kokonoe settle into their life together — until Kento feels Anna's presence.

episodes.name: Strong-willed
episodes.overview: With help from Anna's friends, Kento gets a train ticket to Hakata. But the Peace Organization picks up his scent.

episodes.name: For All Departed Souls
episodes.overview: As the Peace Organization continues its search, a strange boy named Kiriko lets Kento and Anna stay at his house.

episodes.name: The Judgement
episodes.overview: Kaede finds Kento and, alarmed by his living situation, tries to get him to leave with her. But first, she has to deal with his mother.

episodes.name: At All Cost
episodes.overview: As everyone evacuates to escape the rampaging Restoration Daemon, Kento treks back to Hakata to speak to Kiriko directly.
